## Per-project lessons (tasks/lessons.md)

Recommended convention for this project: maintain `tasks/lessons.md` as a running per-project lessons file. Different from `CHANGELOG.md` (universal, tracks WHAT changed) — `tasks/lessons.md` tracks WHY a thing broke and the pattern that prevents recurrence.

Format:
```
## [date] — [short title]
**What happened:** [one sentence]
**Root cause:** [one sentence]
**Pattern that prevents recurrence:** [the rule born from the pain]
```

After ANY correction from Jake: append the lesson here. Review at session start when working in this project. (Pattern borrowed from Boris Cherny's Self-Improvement Loop.)

